Source: organize-includes
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Lenik <organize-includes@bodz.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), python3
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: organize-includes
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: python3-yaml
Description: Reorder and normalize #include directives in C/C++ sources
 organize-includes updates #include paths to be relative to each source
 file and can group/sort includes according to a YAML style file.
 PyYAML (python3-yaml) is recommended when using custom style files (-s).
